'''GCompris''' d yiwen useɣẓan n usegmi ay yesɛan aṭas yiqeddicen i warrac ger 2 d 10 n yiseggasen.

Iqeddiccen-is tikwal d iwuraren, maca yalas d usegmisnen. Ad d-tafem iqeddicen deg yiḥricen yetteddun :

* tiwfit (tagrut) n uselkim : anasiw, amumed, imussa n wamumed, …
* tusnakt : allas n tifelwa (tiduba), uḍḍun, tifelwa s snat yinekcam, tujjurt, …
* tussniwin : tazarurt (trisiti), asinef, allus n waman, tanettabt, …
* tarakalt : sers timura deg tkarḍa
* uraren : tiruẓiyen n uqerruy, tiddest, takatut (tacfawit, timektit), …
* taɣuri : alaɣmu n tɣuri
* nayeḍ : taɣuri n temret (asrag), tijeggirin (tiklutin) yettwassnen s talɣa n puzzle, unuɣ amawayan, asnulfu n tinnaɣ inemussan ...

GCompris yesɛa ugar n 100 yiqeddicen u mazal ar sdat. GCompris d aseɣẓan ilelli, ihi tzemreḍ ad t-tbeddleḍ s lebɣi-k(m) neɣ i usnerni-s, neɣ ahat ad asen-t-tefkeḍ i warrac n umaḍal merra.

